<br>
Anyone?<br>
<br>
A bunch of people are going to find out very, very soon, just how these raid mobs have changed.  It's not going to be perfect for a while for two reasons.<br>
<br>
First, it will take a while for guilds that have been used to having unlimited mana at their disposal to adjust to the new situation.<br>
<br>
Second, no matter how or how little VI playtests these changes, they are going to need to be adjusted.  It will probably be immediately apparent if they make a mob too easy, but given reason #1 above, it will likely be much harder to tell if a mob is too hard or if uber_guild_01 simply can't adjust to the fact that they no longer have the endless river of mana.<br>
<br>
